What do you mind? The ČSSD in Prague does not know and to voldemort or cake
The new councillors of ČSSD in the capital will have to overcome language barriers, it is clear that the components of the board of Prague and the local council to understand their renewed colleagues from the ODS.
The period aktuálně.cz "examined" to the members of the new Council of ČSSD to test their knowledge of the language marked slang that has emerged in recent years in the Council, when they ruled Prague current members of the coalition.
The dictionary encoded using the cream policy of Prague during the previous period, the mayor Pavel bém, includes some of the characters, situations and causes more acquaintances of the metropolis.
Surprisingly, it has been established that the new councillors almost not understand these known concepts.
At least, so they say.
"who is voldemort?"
"The truth is that I do not know."
"rather, I am a rookie in the praguense policy," he said during the examination of terminology of 'colegueo "councillor for culture Lukáš kaucký.
And as regards the political veteran, reacted as Karel Březina.
Perhaps aware of the concept "hole of golf."
"This is potentially the only expression of all that I preguntasteis that use from time to time."
"If it does not normally use slang."
The glossary, whose definitions published the paper aktuálně.cz last June before the Congress to vote on the ODS, chose six examples, in particular those which are particularly connected with the municipal authorities in Prague.
The Socialists had to explain the concepts' voldemort, '"greatest hole of golf of Prague," "go to the cake," "back of bull," "betrayal of the capital" and "shield."
Three councillors agreed to submit to the test and a fourth, antonín weinert, which in future will be responsible for education in Prague, initially agreed, but never again take the phone.
The fifth councillor, Petr dolínek, refused to do so.
"I think in these things and assess how to enjoy themselves the civic democrats."
"What is important to me is how we will understand one another in the execution of our programs," said.
As has been seen, supposedly the councillor Lukáš kaucký had not realised that the title is an expression of an influential businessman and a friend of the former Mayor bém, Roman janoušek.
To kaucký the word 'voldemort "did not mean anything; the only word that he is in" the hole of golf largest of Prague ."
"It is the tunnel blanka," says kaucký immediately, it adds: "but rather what I know about the news."
"I will take that point to a course of languages', joking.
Karel Březina is not the only one which recognises in the hole of golf the tunnel blanka, but also the councillor for the environment Lukáš plachý.
Later, both sociodemócratas know who is really voldemort and Lukáš plachý even knows where to find that character; moreover, suspicion the meaning of "go to the cake."
"I think that means going to a company of Prague"; soon it uncovered plachý to the headquarters of the business of janoušek.
Like Březina, suggests that such knowledge was the news, but that employs just vocabulary.
According to participants in the test, between the sociodemócratas there is no glossary so familiar in colloquial terms.
"I asked my colleagues, but they seem not to have anything like that."
"rather, between us we use nicknames, sometimes abbreviations or do word games with the names," says the President of the ČSSD praguense, Petr hulínský, whose party colleagues call hulda.
"at school I received bříza, but I do not know if my colleagues I also call as well," admits his own nickname Karel Březina.
The newspaper aktuálně.cz tested the name and works.
For his party colleagues, weinert is děda (similar to "yayo") or, less friendly, dědek ("old"), the representative Miroslav poche, which teamed up before the election trickery during the sponsorship of party, is nicknamed "igráček" ("Playmobil") by some of his colleagues.
The nicknames are also the only titles that the sociodemócratas tolerated in the talks in the party.
To hulínský does not like being described as hulda, but the newspaper aktuálně.cz discovered even other nicknames for this President praguense.
"The doctor of the rights of the clubs' it recalls that Petr hulínský received his doctorate in law at the police academy in Bratislava.
The government wants to limit the torture of the "witches," according to published in a pamphlet
Women seen as witches in Burkina Faso share certain characteristics.
They tend to have a great age, they cannot work, for example, for reasons of health, are unmarried and not have children.
Women who are "relapse" witches are sent to an isolated area, not to harm the rest of the people.
"men rarely suffer such but."
"It puts healthy young women, for help in the work and have children," explains a nun who, in the capital of the West African state of Burkina Faso is occupies a special residence of more than 100 women expelled from their communities.
The local government has decided to oppose this unusual "social measure."
Issued an information leaflet which should help to avoid the witch-hunt.
However, this has a drawback.
"more than 70% of adults in Burkina Faso neglects to read," warns the daily, die standard on the disadvantages of awareness in writing.
Accusations of witchcraft are also common in other African countries.
In wins, a neighbouring country of Burkina Faso, the week died ammy hemmah, 72 years, when three women and two men tortured, covered in petrol and burned.
The news appeared on the BBC.
The authors say that was due to an unfortunate series of circumstances.
According to its version, the woman was set in the oil that is used to the unciones rituals.
They set ablaze when the group wanted to "eject bad spirits" of the woman.
The isolation of the "witches" supporters people of all levels of education.
The newspaper Der Standard quoted a businessman of 42 years of Burkina Faso: "the devoradores of human souls always represented a danger," she said.
While in Burkina Faso, the government is trying to appease the witch-hunt, in Gambia last year still participated in it the President.
"The President gambiano jammeh, following the death of his aunt, launched a broad wave of McCarthyism, allegedly had been linked to his death and had tried to kill the President himself through the magic Negro."
"to help him brought to shamans from nearby Guinea, protected by police officers, soldiers and the staff of the President, were to force men and women chosen at random chosen between the peoples gambianos to ownership of the President in kanilai," points out in his report the organization Amnesty International.
In the building, those arrested had to drink a potion of herbs with effects hallucinogens, moreover, are causing intestinal problems and kidney.
Two of those arrested and did not survive the stay on the farm.
Following international pressure, finally released around 1,000 people arrested.
The occupant of bakala: hot stoves with coal and signing a higher rent
The man, aged, and robust, crossed the doors of the centre of attention to the customers of the company byty rpg "tycoon coal" zdeňek bakala, the largest private owner of flats for rent in the Czech Republic.
Under the arm was about documents with the new contracts of hiring Three floors: yours, his daughter and his son, who is serving sentence.
The three I just looting the liberalisation of the rent.
Instead of 3,500 Czech crowns per month, the son will pay starting next year 4.100 crowns for a floor of two rooms with kitchen from second category.
"In addition, it has no hot water and heating is based on a boiler of solid fuel," shows the finger at the man in the new contract of their son, on whose signature has full powers.
"But what I signed," explains means angry, medium resigned.
The civil partnership bytyokd.cz, who described the new conditions of rent as "incorrect and dishonest," recommends to the tenants who do not sign new contracts and to wait until December 7, the date that will publish a guide on how to proceed in such cases.
But, in view of this, the man only just shrug.
"everyone says one thing," says with bad side.
Ostrava is becoming a great laboratory testing of liberalisation.
After New Year would happen with the vast majority of the ones who, in the Czech Republic, were so far under rent regulated.
That is why, aktuálně.cz decided to visit the "laboratory" in person.
The waiting room from rpg is one of the four in Ostrava and, on Tuesday to the nine, was already full.
Just beside the door are the security guards and his side a machine for picking numbers.
"rent 2011," it can be read in a button Luminoso of his touch screen.
The pulsarlo, leaves the machine a papelito with a number.
Almost no time or to read "157" and the number appears on the big screen at the top of the room.
In a second, you are in the queue.
Soon after, a marriage of old age to ask, but the crowd in the room is not here for the new rent.
The majority of people come to solve problems, as usual, applications arrangements, insurance issues and similar matters.
The letters with new rental contracts will arrive in Ostrava in the mail from the tenants of the majority of the 44 apartments belonging to rpg around mid-November.
Rpg byty proposes in letters a rent increase of between 15 and 38%.
On 18 November, opens a window in the centre of attention to customer for the new rent.
"has been in use for a week, so is beginning," respond after hesitating briefly, workers who are in it when the client is presented as a journalist.
The liberalisation and the old flats for miners of bakala are the most delicate issues in the area.
Before the election, as was the loud and clear the Vice-President of Parliament, originating in Ostrava, Lubomír zaorálek, the ČSSD, and now appear in the newspapers of the area.
"twenty years later I would like a new soil."
"neither I changed the damned plate bathroom," desahoga man mentioned in the introduction.
According to the workers, by the time they come mostly retired to see if they get a reduction in rent if you sign in time, as promised by the supply of rpg.
I shall also half of the discount on the rent February the remaining tenants to sign the new contract before 15 December.
However, the window of the 'liberalisation' mining certainly fails to dispel the avalanche of doubts.
"of the 360 customers who were here yesterday, just asked for rent in 2011 around 40 or 50 people," estimated the effect of the window.
Meanwhile, rpg proposes online and on their pieces make individual meetings on contracts when necessary.
If the two sides cannot reach an agreement on the lease, it must resolve the issue of an independent judge.
"This is not a threat, but information about the only way to proceed as possible and in full accordance with the law," warns rpg in its pages.
"here is not going to judge anyone," is one of the pioneering rpg byty and a man in the street opposite the centre of attention to customer gives, at least in part, the reason.
"I receive a pension of 13,000 and I left 5,000 for food; I have no means to go to court," she says.
But, immediately, the employee sows doubt.
"We will see."
"Mr zaorálek warns them in the media not to sign, so perhaps the people expect," she said.
The regulation of rent will no longer exist in the majority of the Czech Republic in early 2011 and, according byty rpg, its increase is an economic necessity.
"The current rent still do not cover even the amounts needed to fund the maintenance of the Community," recalls Pavel klimeš, director of the residential portfolio of the company byty rpg, who adds that the neglected state from the bottom of the Community that enfada to the tenants is, for the owners, the main reason for increasing the rent.
While during the five years between 2005 and 2010 rpg was able to rent apartments to invest in four billion, in the four years that Iran from 2011 to 2014, the number will rise to 5 200 million.
The great screen hanging from the ceiling, as opposed to the seats of the waiting room, now repeats some data highlighted in red.
"The increase in the rent in 2011 in a 15% and less applies to 31.200 apartments, in other words, more than 90% of the properties of rpg."
"In addition, it will always be a maximum 7,50 Czech crowns per month per square metre," indicated on the screen.
Only a 38% increase in rent for 400 flats of the portfolio of rpg.
"in such cases, this is an increase from extremely low amounts of 19,66 Crowns per square metre," suggests rpg.
In 2600 apartment, the lease will stay the same next year.
Rpg byty promises that liberalisation will not affect coup to rents, but escalará between four to eight years.
In addition, the following compromise: the company will invest all the money from the rise of the rent (consult the graph) again in the flats, mainly in saving on heating: new windows and heating.
Have priority people to sign the agreement of rising rent.
The architects have understood that the offices also need childcare
The administrative building avriopoint in Brno is the new headquarters of the company arch.design.
No one would say that is within a small nursery with everything they own to such facilities: walls of colours, furniture creative and even a miniature park in the terrace listening outside.
Since October last year, can go to the children of employees of arch.design.
The company arch.design architectural projects, whose study took numerous buildings known of Brno, thought since the first designs of the building avriopoint in include a space for his miniguardería.
The company employs about 90 people, mainly in the age of the baby boom and allow the arquitectas and delineantes could return soon to work after maternity leave.
Along with the possibility of having a reduced schedule, the nursery is one of the benefits offered by arch.design their workers in the framework of its social agenda.
The builders, and arquitectas thus have the possibility of combining a profession demanding of the care of the children.
The miniguardería was an idea of the employees of arch.designu and, with the support of the leadership, succeeded in obtaining funding from the European Union and the Ministry of Labour and Social Affairs.
The miniguardería enterprise is funded through the European Social Fund in the context of the operational programme for human resources and employment, as well as the budget of the Czech Republic.
Thanks to the funding (an endowment of more than 2.8 million Czech crowns) were able to buy the equipment and, after two years, to recruit qualified staff and services.
When it comes to funding (two years), the company arch.design has the obligation to keep the miniguardería with their own funds over three years.
The preparation of the draft lasted a year and in the presentation of the request for funding helped the company economy rating.
The attention of children is in the hands of qualified personnel; moreover, they are present throughout the day for caring nurse and a teacher of the Ministry of Education. The nursery currently plays host to children with no age limit, although the majority of them have less than three years.
Given that this is a "miniguardería," so can only respond simultaneously to a maximum of five children, but with the shift towards more during the day.
The operation of the nursery is flexible to adapt to the needs of parents and children of all workers have the same right to use the nursery, independently of the hierarchy within the company.
Although this is a lesson and individual care, the content of the programme of the miniguardería are comparable to the programme of the kindergarten.
In her children not only play, but they also receive a quality education: from the basic education to prepare for school, to teach English.
Not only has the kinds of toys and games of table, but also of a computer for children.
The presence of small children in the company itself to create an environment friendly and positive.
Parents can go to see their children at any time and avoid the stress of collect late to children when the school is far from their place of work.
So, parents are more productive while working.
It is not surprising that this would naturally a relationship of trust between the worker and the employer.
In this way, arch.design being signed companies that offer a great advantage for the admission of new workers: support to the family and, in short, this programme reinforced the marketing of staff.
The home of the bone remains fascinando after 100 years of Gaudí internal observed.
The roof looks like the back of a prehistoric lagarto, ladders are reminiscent of the pillar of a dinosaur and the balcony seem to the mouth of a fish open.
So is the Casa batlló, in Barcelona, the architect Antoni Gaudí.
Due to its shape similar to a skeleton, the local apodaron "the home of the bones."
Their organic forms, their glossy colors, the novel use of the stone, the bits of tiles and mosaics, a facade that reminds the scales and the ubiquitous lines mildly curvadas, all this is typical of the secession of Antoni Gaudí.
The front page of the home is playing oneiroid lines, colors and sensitive texturas taken from nature and wildlife.
Paying more attention, there is a certain geometry, pace and a carefully thought.
By the evening, the entire front of the House looks even more impressive, since that is illuminated so that it improves the brightness of the colors.
Serpentea and the torsión of the ways we still surprised in its internal affairs.
The wood ondulada copy of windows, the barandillas, the decorations of the doors, the mirillas and signs.
The Casa batlló, which is in the district of eixample in the number 43 of the lively streets, commercial passeig de grácia, emerged from the renovation of a House of the year 1877 the architect Emilio Chamber courteous.
The reconstruction lasted two years and the home was completed in 1906.
The investor, the rich industrial Josep batlló, initially insisted in overturning the previous building and start from scratch, but soon accepted the idea of Gaudí reconstruction of a novel and cheaper.
However, the Casa batlló, composed of various apartments not devised Antoni Gaudí.
It has assisted in the design of the architect Josep Maria jujol.
Indeed, in their plans for the project emerged ornaments for the apartment is representative of the owner of the property and mosaics used in the facade.
In the front also workers other creators and artists.
The collaboration in the proposals of the Casa batlló was the start of the successful collaboration of jujol with Gaudí.
Jujol participated in the construction of the home milá and park güell of Gaudí, they were in other parts of the same.
Due to their organic form, the premises shortly after their completion the apodaron "the home of the bones."
Others, due to the specific mechanism of opening the windows started to call it 'the home of the yawns. "
It also says that, at the top of the building, the sword of St. George, pattern of Catalonia.
Other elements of the building escultóricos religious motives.
Gaudí projected at home, a single system for the age of central heating, ventilation and air vents and chimneys characteristic.
It may be strange his inclination of forty-five degrees.
During construction, Gaudí did not comply with standards of the time and refused to be influenced by them.
Even so, the building got the relevant permission from the outset, though obviously the data indicated on the planned reconstruction were so vague that, two years after its completion, the city was so shocked by the result which was asked to amend it.
He resented, for example, that the construction included columns even until the public footpaths.
The arrangements were never carried out, quite the contrary: only 15 days after the request of the city, Josep batlló requested (and won) permission to lease the two top floors of the building.
In the lower floors spread the owner.
In the gallery on the second floor in the living room and on the third floor the bedrooms and the private part of the apartment.
The ground floor was hired at a jewellery.
The House, six flats, is completely atravesada by a ladder that leads to the terrace listening to the roof.
The basic elements of the reform were to break all the angles and lines honest, cubriéndolos curved walls.
Gaudí also worked with the modern concept of connection in space.
The common part can connect completely opening the doors of the reception and a larger group can communicate in this way without problems, without renouncing the privacy needed for more intimate.
The House, with the reconstruction of Gaudí, not only won a new facade, but it is also an unusual roof and two additional floors.
It is also amazing how Gaudí plays with light, white and blue tiles that cover the internal courtyard and tragaluces.
The game with the two colours provides maximum of light on all floors of the House.
Was based simply on the principle that the target reflects more light than the dark colours, which instead absorb the rays of sun.
Anyone can visit the Casa batlló, who in 2005 was added to the list of World Heritage of Humanity by UNESCO.
On the first floor of the House is the apartment espacioso more and more of the accessible to the public.
The owners decided to open the doors to the public in 2002, on the occasion of the 150º anniversary of the birth of the famous creator.
With the visitors confirmed, or found, that it is a very good business and widened the visits to the euro zone and to the attic, including the terrace listening to the roof.
The price of entry to the monument is not insignificant, reaches the 16,50 euros, although students, pensioners and the holders of the tourist card gets a 20% discount.
The amount considerably exceeds the price of the entry of other Gaudí building in the city.
If you want to enjoy the real atmosphere of the bed with their towers of lagarto, should be friend quickly from one resident of the neighbouring houses and visit him at home.
How it chooses the mattress and the somier: women and men looking for different things
Nothing of a pompous to bed; what really gives its quality a good bed is the surface to lying down, namely the mattress and the somier.
Above all they must be supplemented to perfection to adapt to specific users.
During the election, there are numerous factors, including the weight, height, state of health and sex of the owner.
It is also important to the kind of Interior for the mattress and the somier.
A typical example?
For example, in a chalet in weekend not ordinarily heating, should not be used because látex cushions are "warm" more slowly.
In addition, usually weighing considerably more than the usual polyurethane cushions.
Therefore, it is necessary to get around more often.
If not properly aired channels of the centre and, above, are on a firm foundation, keep within the moisture. Even moho can appear below.
When choosing a bed, also influence the customs.
Anyone who has spent much time abroad, often uses a mattress very high with a soft layer and will have to be in a lower surface.
"almost all the hockey players who became the NHL complained that there were sleeping just as well."
"for their ground down shoulders, heels and caderas needed cushions with a soft layer of viscoelástica."
"This kind of cushions also are recommended for people with diabetes that time problems of the nervous system, so that they are wrong information of expression and of the skin," explains hadamcziková Sylva, which specializes in the acolchado furniture.
Many hockey players, like other customers, time-consuming preferring the viscoelástica cushions.
"Today there is no longer a problem, because they have these suitable tempur and Italians magniflex, but also the Czech brand tropico."
There is no longer to be a player in the NHL to see the viscoelástica.
This "miracle" is very simple.
Optimises its rigidity and form of the heat absorbed or adapts to its body heat.
Nothing presses; during the night, will not cycling as after a hard game.
Simply, they slept better.
The viscoelástica doubles as protection against the wounds.
By choosing the size of the buffer, add up the length of their feet, namely between 21 and 34 cm.
A man or woman with a height of about 180 cm will need a bed of between 210 and 220 cm.
The minimum width for one should be, in a double room, 90 cm, in total 180 cm.
In the case of individual rooms, for example of singles recommends at least between 120 and 140 cm.
For a possible visit is also comfortable.
"If not, you can apply a standard simple to calculate the wide: the lying down their should have their hands encogidas comfortably to the elbow," advises the ingeniera Helena prokopová, informed of cechu čalouníků to dekoratérů, which already has many years to manage the issue of healthy sleep and the ergonomics of the furniture, who teaches in specialist schools.
In twin rooms, each one needs its own somier and mattress, so during the purchase attention should be paid to combine the height of the cushions.
Otherwise, it will be necessary to put on the somieres to different heights, which is not always possible in all the beds.
The foam cushions should have a minimum height of 14 cm, models with interior of docks a minimum of 15 cm, of which at least three inch are for the layer that adapts to the forms and relaxing.
"in touch with the hand or in the mattress, certainly should not be noticed the docks," warns Helena prokopová.
Each mattress requires a kind of somier determined.
The bedrooms acolchados completely, in which the mattress and the basis are as siameses, does not make sense in the bedroom.
The cushions are breathing wrong and you cannot wash their forms, which today is often.
And, given that every night transpiramos between 0.2 and 0.75 l of sweat, it is clear that after about five or seven years the bed will begin to remind a great (and crowded) point of view.
For this reason, experts reject the slogans that talk of a life of buffer of up to 25 years or, even, of a guarantee for life.
However, there is a but.
So, sellers give a Council: in the cushions with a width of 120 or 140 cm, carefully ensure cleaning and brainwashing the forms, but better adds a protective buffer that they can be easily and launder.
Although currently being built fundas of cushions with closure one-for-one system on its shores, so the course are in two parts (something very important to money laundering and the size of the washing machine!), his intervention in the larger models (and for a single person) to lift the mattress can seem a fight between a fly weight and a heavyweight.
In bed, instead of a somier, does a firm?
Never!
As for the beds designed to a night visitors.
However, it must make (if you do not already) ventilation holes in the table and must be used with a mattress with docks in the interior and a minimum height of 15 cm with the docks in pockets (like the German taschenfederkern) and a soft layer.
The cushions them should not be used on such databases.
For the somieres of thin not articulables and containing between 14 and 18 thin, can be used látex cushions or sandwich cushions (for example, a combination of látex fibre and Coco), although it is always best to somier with a greater number of thin, 28 or more, in which the thin the lumbar area are strengthened and could regulate its rigidity.
The somieres of thin articulables should not be used with a cushion of docks, since we do not react to the reclinación.
In addition to the adjustment of the rigidity of the thin, it can also use the protection of the shoulders.
This is a special area of the thin that allows press or, even, tip the thin so that "around him" perfectly to the shoulders during sleep.
For men who have a very broad shoulders, this is something very important.
Even remember them manufacturers of cushions that, in the "male," began to use a softer precisely around the shoulders.
Also remember women, for which have a softer around the caderas.
For the most demanding customers, there are somieres structure in Cruz or tablets with the so-called dampening multitorsión.
The pressure was distributed among different points and reduce tension.
It must also note that, although using the mattress and somier adequate if you use a pillow (large and "mullida"), will the majority of the benefits.
The basic rule is simple: the pillow must underlie the head and the corner can only reach the shoulders, so that we can relax the muscles of the same.
The right size recommended is 50 X 60 cm, something normal, for example in Scandinavia.
The lying down aside, the pillow must be at the same level, when combined with the somier with reinforcement to shoulders or the softer area of bed) that the height of the shoulders.
The modern cushions have something to do, it seems, with the original cushions stuff of straw.
The manufacturers are using increasingly often, natural materials or, at least, mixtures.
In fact, they are fashionable the biological cushions.
The raw materials from oil, which manufactures the polyurethane foam, be completed with natural oils, for example of ricino or soya.
Indeed, virtually all manufacturers employ known soya.
"organic, in the case of the cushions, mean that the center is made solely of natural materials," explains Petr vašíček enterprise tropico plus.
In addition, natural substances are used in the manufacture of the forms of the cushions, one of the first aloe Vera.
But it can also be opting for the microcápsulas, who released a fresh aroma of wood or lavanda.
There are also differences for men and women.
While the men were "refrescan" with plant extracts of breeze, to which the forms of mattress absorbing heat and refresque the body, women prefer "heat" the forms.
The extract of red toss enhances the circulation of blood, so that women feel more warmth.
Does favourites today?
The cushions made of foam, which are more porous, with a structure of cells tailored, which makes them more permeable than normal polyurethane and offer more permeability.
The combination of various rigidities of cold and viscoelástica enable manufacture foam cushions of various areas which they know perfectly well where is head, shoulders and the heels.
A buffer of good quality will cost of seven thousand kroner up.
Those that have a therapeutic role often have a lower VAT, because they are considered as health resources.
The first thing we got this advantage in the Czech Republic was gumotex.
It is difficult to save in the cushions and somieres.
Sometimes it can approve the proposals put forward by manufacturers or sellers, which sometimes offer two cushions for the price of one.
For example, the designation magniflex offers duofreeze cushions with a memory foam memory affixed to the founded by 11.990 crowns.
The second is to be achieved for free.
The era of the viscoelástica with an open cell structure and a high density began with the "cósmico tempur material."
Initially emerged as material for NASA, because during landing astronauts eulogies were subjected to a huge burden.
Tempur is ablanda with the heat and tighten.
Consequently, the human body, warm, exerts a perfect effect and best suited their pressure.
Therefore, it is ideal to avoid wounds, but also to improve comfort for the dream.
The foam viscoelástica not only used in the cushions, but also for medicinal products, for example to almohadas that is injected under the legs and the ease, as well as their movement.
Domestic manufacturers, for example, use foam eucatherm C or twinsaver and the like.
More and more parents used monitoring devices in people to control their children.
The fear for the children has been more and more people to monitor them remains with by GPS.
The system, initially thought in the monitoring of vehicles, which can also follow the movement of people and thus contribute, for example, in case such as the disappearance of the nine-year-old girl anička janatková.
By the time the device is the size of a box of cerillas, but soon it will reduce the size of a clock.
Many people gave fear the case of the defunct anička and began reporting on the means available to best protect their children.
Even at the expense of invading their privacy.
"we all try to tell us that this is not about spying, but another way to reduce the chances of a tragedy," believes Petr pilin enterprise macro Weil, one of the suppliers of monitoring devices in the Czech market.
"I recognise that, in certain cases, be of such devices, for example if they get into the bag of someone without their knowledge, but we have not yet come up with such cases."
"The majority of customers actually buy for safety reasons," adds pilin.
In his opinion, children should always know what the point of the "cajita" and how it is used in case of emergency.
Child psychologist Dana bočková draws attention to the fact that, if the child does not want to take it, simply throw away.
"even the younger children show great creativity to intentionally lose certain things if they want to avoid being monitored."
"before, parents relied greatly on mobiles, but these could be turning off as easily as the monitoring device," says bočková.
In his view, it is debatable whether in case of attack this arrangement is genuinely useful.
"If this is a kidnapping, the author almost always will check if the child has, for some kind of electronic device that can unveil its location."
"Now is the telephone."
"We are going to extend the use of the devices, also the will, since its sale will surely be much publicity."
"in such cases, the criminals are always a step ahead of the police," says psychologist.
However, adds that such devices can help in the case of an attack from an improvised.
According to Robert čech enterprise RC monitoring, which provides services for monitoring both for vehicles and for people, even if, after an attack, destroying the monitoring device, its presence can be of help.
"can the device for which regularly sends the position after a certain period."
"If suffering damage, at least the latest position of the person in question."
"the most expensive devices have included an medidor slopes, so if the person is simply resbala and stays put, the device will issue an immediate warning with the position in question," says čech.
In his opinion, a service of this kind can be obtained with mobile phones with intelligent navigation, in which only has set up a special software.
The problem of the current monitoring units is that by the time these devices with a similar size to a box of cerillas or mobile phones to smaller.
Therefore, could be lost.
According to pilin of macro Weil, for that reason we are testing now with devices that resemble a digital clock.
"In addition, they will have the added advantage of a potential attacker may not identify the device."
"or that identify it after some time, which may make the police earn time," it adds.
Although the monitoring devices are put in the doll or hanging will be using the same technology used for monitoring of vehicles.
It is checking the position with a GPS system (which is used in navigation in the car) combined with the function of a cell phone that the current position.
