A survey uncovered ridiculous rules.
The survey of absurdity is part of the year for the fourth time in the tournament business.
He has already made some ridiculous rules.
The unknown winner of the new edition of the survey absurdity of the year was the obligation to bring the administration to documents that officials can access online.
The decision is adopted more than a third of the nearly four thousand voters.
For example, the social security administration called a text from the commercial register, although their officials can be accomplished with two movements of the mouse.
Thanks to the survey, this has changed.
"The Czech administration of social security no longer will an extract from trade register when out of the impositions of the insured," said the spokesman for čssz Jana buraňová.
The aim of the absurdity of the year is to consult the rules and regulations that must respect businesses and entrepreneurs in the Czech Republic, and to try to erase those that are absurd.
This year, form part of the tournament for the fourth time publishing business hospodářské noviny and begins to create fashion also among the general public.
While the edition last year with the involvement of three thousand voters this year virtually reached four thousand.
And it is not surprising, since we still have plenty of several legal obligations that must be respected just to trade.
"perhaps in number of documents to the declaration of taxes we are first of the world," says Karel havlíček of the Association of small and medium-sized enterprises and entrepreneurs of the Czech Republic.
For years, the simplification of business rules is a stated objective of all governments.
However, in comparison with the rest of the world, the situation of improvement, especially in the Czech Republic.
According to the World Bank, from the point of view of the conditions for a company, the Czech Republic is in the position 74ª, i.e. eight posts worse than last year.
The absurdity of the year was held for the first time in 2006 and each year in the same way.
Anyone can suggest any administrative or bureaucratic absurdity every year between April and the end of September, when it closes the competition.
The proposals might be made to the website www.firmaroku.cz. later, the organiser of the contest to choose seven candidates for the "antipremio" and, in October, allows the public to vote on the Internet through www.firmaroku.cz / absurdita and www.ihned.cz.
Wins the absurdity that receives more votes.
For the survey this year there were more than a hundred, in particular 105 rules and regulations that are meaningless.
The examples them both employers and professional associations and journalists.
Among the "rose" of the competition was framed, for example, the requirement for vehicles to the maintenance of roads and motorways pay tolls or that employers with 20 employees, two offices and two bathrooms painted every two years the walls.
The list of the 1970s proposals this year is published in the pages of the competition.
The announcement of the contest, which always takes place in early November in Wenceslas Square in Prague, is part of an event at the usually involved Celebrities from political and social.
This year, for example, attended this act of tender Eva svobodová, director of the Association of small and medium-sized enterprises and entrepreneurs of the Czech Republic, or Petr kužel, President of the Chamber of Commerce in the Republic.
"economic prosperity cannot stand if the state puts continuously obstacles to entrepreneurs, so my aim is to eliminate every year a minimum of 30 paragraphs that currently unnecessarily complicate trade," announced by the Minister of Industry and Commerce Martin kocourek.
Efforts to eliminate the absurd regulations are not left in tatters.
In 2007, what more annoyed people was the duty of the employer of communicating with an advance of three days in the business office of the area of operation, the intention of taking a post to a show or exhibition.
This obligation is removed in the new law.
The requirement that ended up in second place in the number of votes in 2007, namely the communication to the office to work for part of its foreign workers of the journeys of up to 30 days, it was deleted in the law of the so-called green card.
And the third is the back.
The absurdity of the year 2009 was the regulation for the physiotherapists have in their consultation a large mirror, a fridge and two speaking of soil.
That is why, this year the Ministry of Health issued a statement saying that he had removed the obligation to have a fridge.
