This year, a travelling salesman sandías of Shanghai suffered brain damage after a row with five officers.
A video game full of violence, available for download online, presents inspectors trained by the Chinese who attack street sellers.
"chengguan has left a scar on the government," deplores China Daily, a national publication, last year after another controversy over tactics.
The newspaper demanded "a really thorough cleansing."
Skeptics say that the current approach is very far from this.
