But noted that the demands were high standards in many reminders of Chinese work for both sexes.
Then comes the demand for armoniosos facial features.
If this means be bet, it is a matter of debate among the Chinese.
Surely, the handicapped or disfigured must not stand.
"We cannot allow a person to take or a jorobado come to work here," said Mr Zheng.
"his image it would be wrong."
