She does not believe that the emphasis in your appearance is sexist, said.
"Do you think it is sexy with this?" he asked with a look sardónica.
His colleague with hoyuelos, Xu Yang, 21, said "our work must submit the image of the city."
They do not oppose its work at the time, they said, because entertained ambitions to race higher than simply scare sellers in the alleys where it was supposed to stop his business.
