Nicolas Sarkozy and less still.
A mandate in the Élysée Palace leads to another.
Therefore, the current head of state will be a candidate in 2012.
However, this does not combine well with the mystery that is generally associated with the presidential role.
Therefore, there is always that appear to question.
To one side and to the other.
In 2006, although it creyesen, the friends of Jacques Chirac stated that not ruling out a third term.
