Is it the official announcement of his candidacy?
Not much less.
The President just indicated that the constitutional reform of 2008 restricted to two the number of terms of five years.
Simply sent the facts, not an announcement.
It is not the first time that speaks of presidential ones, with a humorous note, at meetings of this kind.
"in the worst, or rather of the cases, still pasaréis seven and a half years with me," had unleashed in July 2009.
On another occasion, in May 2010: "No penséis that I wonder what will follow."
